high_descs: Move to the counter that is between the stove and the fridge.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the counter.
Turn around and move to the counter that is on the left of the sink.
Slice the apple that is on the counter.
Turn around and move to the counter that is on the left side of the stove.
Put the butter knife back on the counter.
Move across the room to the sink.
Pick up an apple slice off of the counter.
Turn around and move to the fridge.
Open the fridge. Place the apple slice inside to cool.  CLose the door.  Open the door and remove the apple.
Move to the counter between the fridge and the stove.
Place the apple on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Use knife to slice apple.  Cool apple to be placed on counter near stove.

high_descs: turn around and walk to the kitchen counter next to the refrigerator
grab the butter knife off of the counter
turn around and walk to the kitchen counter next to the coffee maker
cut the apple on the counter
turn around and walk to the kitchen counter you were at previously
place the knife on the potato
turn around and walk to the other kitchen counter
grab an apple slice off of the counter
turn around and walk to the refrigerator
place the apple slice inside of the refrigerator, then take it back out
walk to the kitchen counter
place the apple slice on the counter in front of you
Turn right, walk some, then turn right and face the counter with the knife on it.
Grab the knife from the counter.
Turn right, turn right again and walk to the left side of the sink.
Slice the apple into 3 pieces.
Turn around back to the counter the knife was on.
Place the knife on the right side of the counter on top of the potato.
Walk back to the sliced up apple on the counter.
Grab one slice of the apple
Turn right, then turn right again and walk to the fridge.
Place the slice into the fridge and chill it for 5 seconds. Remove the slice.
Move back to the counter on the right.
Place the apple slice on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled apple slice on the counter.
